name: Zubababanchou - Gagaga Coat
desc: If you control a "Zubaba" or "Gagaga" monster except "Zubababanchou - Gagaga Coat": You can Special Summon this card from your hand. You can target 1 "Gogogo" or "Dododo" monster in your GY; Special Summon it, but for the rest of this turn, you cannot Special Summon monsters from the Extra Deck, except Xyz Monsters. You can only use each effect of "Zubababanchou - Gagaga Coat" once per turn.
